{"tid":1615842,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急：蒙面法大方向 ［文宣要人］","createTime":"2019-10-03T08:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T09:31:38.000Z","uid":268462,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b70cda20e3687258c0ab93d8ced9e300a1eb92","tid":1615842,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:15:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得政府未決定好係咪實行 想睇今日股市表現再判斷引用緊急法實施蒙面法對股市有幾大影響<br />\n<br />\n而政府宜家考慮既因素只係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國際聲譽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n蒙面法係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔會</span></span>令到外資驚㗎 實際上好多西方國家都有蒙面法 包括美國加拿大法國等等 但主要針對恐怖組織同埋打壓宗教公開表態<br />\n<br />\n所以核彈係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊急法</span></span> 外資公司唔知政府會唔會再以緊急法通過各種會影響到佢地既法例 <br />\n<br />\n所以宜家要話俾外國知 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊急法有幾恐怖</span></span> 由外國傳媒/外資公司施壓<br />\n<br />\n時間唔係淨返好多！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xVR0p0T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxVR0p0T.png&h=a944cee0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7dc1879a5343fca0b79ef3945333f44ca046949","tid":1615842,"uid":284419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"將蒙面變做日常...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615829</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e6872c6277b33372567690af3458ee788b5d9f81","tid":1615842,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"幫手推！"},{"pid":"abe090b217d34b2f0859f31c530f496d10a5ea76","tid":1615842,"uid":35470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7dc1879a5343fca